com.vmware.vapi

Class VapiFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.VapiFactory

  • public class VapiFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    VapiFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.vapi package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.

      • metadata

        public MetadataFactory metadata()
        The com.vmware.vapi.metadata package provides metadata interfaces. These are interfaces that provide different facets of API information. Clients can use these interfaces to:
        • Discover APIs available in the infrastructure.
        • Fetch metadata that can be used to build presentation layers like CLI, REST, etc.
        • Fetch authentication and authorization metadata.
